ition `Multiset.card (parts.filter (· ≠ 0)) ≤ N` holds because the number of nonzero parts is at most N. The bijection proofs require function extensionality on `Fin N` for the forward direction and multiset equality for the reverse. We will need the following Mathlib facts: `Nat.Partition` structure (already available), `Multiset.card`, `Multiset.filter`, `Multiset.sort`, `List.Pairwise`, `Finset.univ`, `Finset.card`, `Finset.filter`. Also need `ext` lemma for `NPartition`.",
